---
import MizuLayout from '@/layouts/MizuLayout.astro'
---

<MizuLayout
  title="System Status | Pixelated Empathy"
  description="Operational status information for Pixelated Empathy."
>
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="site-shell site-shell--narrow relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white"
        >
          System Status
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          A public real-time status feed is not published yet. During pilots and
          evaluations, operational updates are shared directly with the teams
          involved.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 mb-12">
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Operational updates</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            We share rollout and incident communication directly with active
            evaluation partners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Security questions</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Teams that need deployment or support expectations can contact us
            directly for the current operating picture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Status history</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            We are avoiding placeholder uptime claims until a public status
            workflow is actually in place.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Need an update?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          If you are evaluating the platform or waiting on a specific
          operational detail, send a note and we will answer directly.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25 hover:shadow-primary-500/40 hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Contact us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MizuLayout>
